Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.44,Normal,,0,0,0,,... vào bạn đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.44,Normal,,0,0,0,,Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.57,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,Moka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:02.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:04.98,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tsukune!
