Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.97,Normal,,0,0,0,,Phải chăng ... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.06,Normal,,0,0,0,,Hỗn xược!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,Moka-san? Đợi đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,Yukari, Mizore! Hãy bảo vệ Tsukune!
